      <title>Abrdn 押注中国长期债券，10 年期收益率目标为 1%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/abrdn-bets-on-chinese-long-bonds-with-10-year-yield-target-of-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Abrdn Plc 表示，由于根深蒂固的通货紧缩压力和进一步放松货币政策的前景，中国不断飙升的长期债券仍然值得买入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/abrdn-bets-on-chinese-long-bonds-with-10-year-yield-target-of-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 01:35:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
