    <item>
      <title>贝索斯与特朗普不和，但现在需要马斯克的太空竞赛帮助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/bezos-feuded-with-trump-but-now-needs-help-in-space-race-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊的 Starlink 卫星竞争对手柯伊伯计划面临延迟。亚马逊创始人杰夫·贝佐斯是唐纳德·特朗普第一任期内攻击的对象，现在他采取了和解态度，预计将与当选总统会面讨论该项目。布鲁斯·艾因霍恩在“彭博科技”上发表了更多报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/bezos-feuded-with-trump-but-now-needs-help-in-space-race-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 01:19:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度影子银行 Shriram 为该行业寻求创纪录的离岸贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/indian-shadow-bank-shriram-seeks-record-offshore-loan-for-sector</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Shriram Finance Ltd. 正就一笔约 12.5 亿美元的社会贷款进行深入谈判，这笔交易将成为印度影子银行有史以来最大的离岸贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/indian-shadow-bank-shriram-seeks-record-offshore-loan-for-sector</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 01:17:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
